Title: From Africa to Europe
DateModified: '2019-03-10'
DatePublished: '2019-03-10'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/from-africa-to-europe
SetInCountry: South Africa
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Siseko Yelani
AuthorCountry: South Africa
Text: Africa is know to be a unique destination, offering culture, wildlife and other
  natural phenomenals but little is known by most Africans about European destinations
  such as Portugal. Many have accepted their feit on they will never be able to travel
  into Europe due to their economic distress and weak local currency throughout the
  African continent. Connection between Africa and many European countries dates back
  to more than a century, the devastating Slave trade between the respective continents
  may have created a bitter sweet perceptions of then oppressed continent by the other.
